source.name: 2005-2009 American Community Survey 5-Year Estimates Summary File Tracts and Block Groups
source.description: A nationwide survey that collects information such as age, race, income, commute time to work, home value, veteran status, and other data. Data from the American Community Survey and the Puerto Rico Community Survey were collected during calendar years 2005- 2009. Data available at the  block group level.
